other way but Turn or Die. <lb/>
O what's the matter then that <lb/>
the hearts of sinners be not pierced <lb/>
with such a weighty truth! A <lb/>
man would think now, that every <lb/>
Unconverted soul that hears these <lb/>
words, should be pricked to the <lb/>
