three things. <lb/>
First, he is one who <normalised orig="placeth" auto="true">places</normalised> his <lb/>
chief content on earth, and <normalised orig="loveth" auto="true">loves</normalised> <lb/>
the creature more then God, and <lb/>
his fleshly prosperity above the <lb/>
