O Sirs, Conversion is another <lb/>
kind of work then most are ware <lb/>
of: Its not a small matter to bring <lb/>
an Earthly mind to Heaven, and <lb/>
to <normalised orig="shew" auto="true">show</normalised> man the amiable excellencies <lb/>
of God, till he be taken up in <lb/>
such Love to him, that never can <lb/>
