Religion, and yet be going still to <lb/>
the <choice ana="illegible">
                     <sic>*<normalised orig="ame" auto="true">am</normalised></sic>
                     <corr>same</corr>
                  </choice> End as before, intending <lb/>
his carnal Self above all, and giving <lb/>
it still the Government of his <lb/>
soul. But when he is Converted, <lb/>
this Self is <normalised orig="denyed" auto="true">denied</normalised> and taken <lb/>
