Eternity, Eternity, will be the <lb/>
                  <choice ana="illegible">
                     <sic>me*sure</sic>
                     <corr>measure</corr>
                  </choice> of your <normalised orig="Joyes" auto="true">Joys</normalised> or sorrows, <lb/>
